Karl Stefanovic's blue suit is now world famous after the internet went 'a little bit crazy' over the fact the television presenter had been wearing the same thing every day for a year.

The Today show co-host has worn the exact same cheap Burberry suit on air to prove a point about the double standards women face, especially in the television industry.

Stefanovic said he had not received one complaint about his repetitive attire over the past year, but his female co-host Lisa Wilkinson regularly copped criticism about the way she looked. 

